descriptionHTML:
Ukrainian Flag Watch Face is the best Watch Face ever! Just download this watch face and you will always have your favourite flag showing the time on your hand! The flag design is made in material design style so you will be fashionable and modern! I love you Ukraine!

Features:
•  beautiful and modern design.
•  working perfectly on both round and square watches.
•  you can see your favourite flag perfectly designed in ambient and ambient low bit modes.
•  compatible with most popular smartwatches: Moto 360, LG G Watch R, LG G Watch, Sony Smartwatch 3, Samsung Gear Live, Asus ZenWatch, LG Watch Urbane and many others.
comments: Great watch face Just wish there were more ways to customize but otherwise it's great
